6_20	0.0	``If the trees died, that would ruin the place''.
6_21	0.0	The question is whether the ladybugs, which usually feast on aphids, will eat enough of the psyllids to make a difference.
6_22	0.0	``They're nice to have, and they may eat some of the psyllids, but I don't think you'll see a serious drop in the population,'' said Garrison.
6_23	0.0	He said further studies must be done to find out what insects attack the psyllids in their Australian home.
