8_0	0.0	&QL; &UR; SALINAS, Calif.
8_1	0.0	_ &LR; Tom Jones is a hands-on farmer, not some touchy-feely type with sentimental ideas about Mother Nature and her eternal wisdom.
8_2	0.0	Yet Jones listens to his strawberry plants which, he asserts, change every day.
8_3	0.0	You get in trouble when you interfere with their natural cycle and try to make the plants do what &LR; you &LR; want, he says.
8_4	0.0	At the same time, the co-owner of Windward Farming Co.
